descriptionHtml:
Added a version for default hair if you don\'t want to install the hair mod. Check images for default hair version.

This is my second attempt for a request I got a long time ago. This is an imperial inspired by Megan Fox. I failed pretty bad on my last version of Megan and wanted to get it right before I uploaded any new characters. It took a few different mods but I think I\'ve come up with something much more acceptable (my last version was just all around ugly). Hope you guys like it!

Save is level 1 after the dragon attack and her race is Imperial.

Required Mods:
Better Females by Bella- http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2812
Coolsims Hair Pack- http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3809

I\'m only uploading the save file, to install these mods visit the pages and follow their instructions.



My next character will be Thor. Leave a comment if you have any requests or suggestions.




[center]If you liked this check out my other characters[/center]
